    Description
    Appointments
    This class is used to store and access Appointments data.
    Contacts
    This class represents a contact object containing the name, contact email, and contact id.
    Countries
    This class represents a country object containing the country id and the country name.
    Customers
    This class represents a customer object containing the customer id, customer name, customer address, customer phone, customer postal code, division id, and division name.
    First_Level_Divisions
    This class represents the first level divisions object containing the division id, division name, and country id.

    This class contains information about the location of appointments.
    Times
    This class serves to represent times and months.
    Types
    The Types class contains methods that allows the database table to be filled with valid types.
    Users
    The Users class is a model object and represents a registered user in the system.
